research/history/logs/agent_action_0104.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","reference_round":103,"env_overrides":[{"key":"NUM_EXPERTS","value":"64"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_shared(x)} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E(x)} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 B^sh 是始终激活的静态 shared 子库，E(x) 是轻量 router 选出的少量 routed experts，所有原子都来自静态向量库，因此在线侧仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared 子库查表 + routed 子库查表 + 有限加权和”链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容。唯一主假设：r103 已证明 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 能稳定训练并在约 total_cost=0.63x 取得 FVU=0.1188，接下来最有信息量的问题是它是否仍受 routed 总容量限制；相对 r103 仅把 `NUM_EXPERTS: 32 -> 64`，保持 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 的短激活路径与其余 recipe 不变，如果 shared+routed MoE-like 方向确实值得继续，则应在几乎同一成本带（fresh cost 约 selection=0.52x、deployment=0.12x、total=0.64x）进一步压低 FVU。","summary":"沿 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 做第一次真实容量扩展 probe：相对 r103 只增大 `NUM_EXPERTS`，直接判断 shared+routed 结构在保持短 active path 时是否还有 sparse-capacity 收益。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r103 只改 `NUM_EXPERTS`。这不是回到旧 family 的 K 轴细扫，而是对刚验证可运行的新 MoE-like family 做最核心的结构问题测试；同时 fresh cost 已核对仍明显低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","needs_sanity":true,"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["r103 已确认 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 可稳定训练，最近两轮 crash 不是该 family 前向/反向实现问题。","本轮以 r103 为 reference，只改 `NUM_EXPERTS=64`，用于判断 shared+routed 结构是否仍受 routed static capacity 限制。","fresh cost 估算：`shared_routed_expert_topk K=128 EF=1 NUM_EXPERTS=64` 的 selection≈0.52x、deployment≈0.12x、total≈0.64x，仍在允许的 0.3x-0.8x 结构 anchor 带内。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `NUM_EXPERTS=64` 明显优于 r103，则 shared+routed 路线值得继续，下一步再考虑叠加 low-rank trunk。","如果结果与 r103 接近或更差，则说明 trunk-free shared+routed 线已接近饱和，后续不应继续把预算投在这条 family 的容量扩张上。","如果本轮再次出现参数落地异常，应优先检查 round config 与 checkpoint config 中 `num_experts=64` 是否真实生效，再决定是否继续该 family。"]}
research/history/round_summaries/round_0136.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\uff1ax_hat = \u03a3_{i\u2208S_{e*(x)}(x)} \u03b1_i(x) b_{e*(x),i}\uff0c\u7b49\u4ef7\u5730\u4e5f\u53ef\u5199\u6210 x_hat = \u03a3_e \u03a3_{i\u2208S_e(x)} 1[e=e*(x)] \u03b1_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}\u3002\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u5728\u7ebf\u94fe\u8def\u662f\u201c\u8f7b\u91cf router \u9009 1 \u4e2a\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93 -> \u8be5\u5b50\u5e93\u5185 local top-k -> \u9759\u6001\u5411\u91cf\u67e5\u8868\u52a0\u6743\u548c\u201d\uff1b\u9759\u6001\u5e93\u4e0d\u968f\u6837\u672c\u52a8\u6001\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64 `expert_topk` \u5c5e\u4e8e\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\u3002`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u8fd9\u7c7b batch/sample-coupled family \u5c5e\u4e8e\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9\uff0c\u53ea\u4fdd\u7559\u5386\u53f2\u53c2\u8003\uff0c\u4e0d\u8fdb\u5165\u5f53\u524d frontier\u3002\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\uff1a\u76f8\u5bf9 r25 \u4ec5\u628a `NUM_EXPERTS` \u63d0\u5230 128\uff0c\u53ef\u5728\u4fdd\u6301 `K=128` \u4e0e `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` \u7684\u77ed\u6fc0\u6d3b\u8def\u5f84\u4e0b\uff0c\u628a routed-only \u603b\u9759\u6001\u5bb9\u91cf\u63a8\u5230\u4e0e\u5f53\u524d\u4f4e\u6210\u672c `shared_routed_expert_topk` \u6700\u4f18\u70b9\u8fd1\u4f3c matched-cost \u7684 0.41x \u533a\u95f4\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u56de\u7b54 shared \u5206\u652f\u662f\u5426\u771f\u6709\u5fc5\u8981\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0136.json:41:      "\u5982\u679c\u8be5\u70b9\u5728\u7ea6 0.41x \u4e0b\u63a5\u8fd1\u6216\u4f18\u4e8e\u5f53\u524d `shared_routed_expert_topk K=128` \u7684 FVU=0.1010\uff0c\u5219\u4e0b\u4e00\u8f6e\u53ef\u56f4\u7ed5\u8fd9\u4e2a routed-only recipe \u505a\u8fdb\u4e00\u6b65\u538b\u7f29\uff0c\u4f8b\u5982\u4ee5\u65b0\u70b9\u4e3a reference \u53ea\u6539 `K` \u6216 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`\u3002",
