research/history/logs/agent_action_0103.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","reference_round":100,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_routed_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_shared(x)} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E(x)} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 B^sh 是始终激活的静态 shared 子库，E(x) 是轻量 router 选出的少量 routed experts，所有原子都来自静态向量库，因此在线侧仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared 子库查表 + routed 子库查表 + 有限加权和”链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容。唯一主假设：最近两轮的重复 crash 更像训练链路仍在按旧 allowlist 校验 action 级 env_overrides，而不是 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 前向/反向实现本身有问题；因此相对 r100 只切换 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_routed_expert_topk`、复用稳定参考配方中已验证可运行的其余参数，作为最小健康检查来确认当前系统能否真正启动该 family。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果该最小健康检查能启动并产出有效训练结果，再回到显式 `NUM_EXPERTS/ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 的 shared+routed recipe 做结构验证。","如果该最小健康检查仍被同类 pipeline error 拦截，则应把根因上收为训练控制器/校验缓存未刷新，而不是继续修改 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 本体实现。","如果该最小健康检查通过但质量很弱，下一步再决定是否给 shared+routed 结构叠 low-rank trunk，而不是继续在 trunk-free 版本上细扫。"],"notes_to_memory":["Round 103 先不再重复显式传 `NUM_EXPERTS/ACTIVE_EXPERTS`，改用相对 r100 只切 `ARCHITECTURE` 的最小健康检查，确认系统状态。","若本轮成功启动，则说明最近两轮 crash 主要来自 action-level override 校验链，而不是 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 架构实现。","若本轮仍报同类 pipeline error，应优先调查长生命周期控制器是否仍使用旧的 override allowlist/缓存。"],"self_review":"符合工程修复优先级：不新开 family，不改 optimizer/lr/loss/preprocess，只对最近失败 family 做最小健康检查。相对 reference_round=100 仅改一个 env 参数 `ARCHITECTURE`，归因最清晰。","summary":"对最近连续两轮 crash 的 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 做最小健康检查：复用 r100 的稳定配方，只切 architecture，先确认当前训练链路是否能真正启动该 family。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/round_summaries/round_0159.json:7:  "family_name": "shared_routed_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0159.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4fdd\u6301\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_{i\u2208S_shared(x)} \u03b1_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + \u03a3_{e\u2208E(x)} \u03a3_{j\u2208S_e(x)} \u03b1_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}\u3002\u5176\u4e2d shared \u5b50\u5e93 B^sh \u4e0e routed expert \u5b50\u5e93 {B_e} \u90fd\u662f\u9759\u6001\u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff0c\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u53ea\u505a\u8f7b\u91cf router \u9009\u62e9\u5c11\u91cf routed experts\uff0c\u7136\u540e\u6267\u884c shared \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 + routed \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 + \u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u53ef\u76f4\u63a5\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5224\u65ad\u4e3a\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u8fd9\u7c7b batch/sample-coupled family \u4ecd\u660e\u786e\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8 frontier\u3002\u5f53\u524d `<0.25x` \u4e3b\u6218\u573a\u91cc\uff0cr115\u2192r116 \u5df2\u8bc1\u660e `shared_routed_expert_topk` \u5728\u4fdd\u6301 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` \u7684\u524d\u63d0\u4e0b\u6cbf width \u8f74\u5de6\u79fb\u4ecd\u6709\u7ed3\u6784\u4fe1\u53f7\uff0c\u800c r114 \u53c8\u7ed9\u51fa\u6e05\u6670\u8d1f\u4fe1\u53f7\uff1a\u628a `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` \u538b\u5230 1 \u867d\u80fd\u5230\u7ea6 0.20x\uff0c\u4f46 FVU \u4f1a\u9000\u5316\u5230 0.2038\u3002\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\u662f\uff1a\u76f8\u5bf9 r116 \u4ec5\u628a `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` \u4ece 192 \u518d\u538b\u5230 160\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_routed_expert_topk`\u3001`K=64`\u3001`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`\u3001`NUM_EXPERTS=64` \u4e0e\u5176\u4f59\u8bad\u7ec3\u914d\u65b9\u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u53ef\u4ee5\u628a total_cost \u4ece\u7ea6 0.22x \u518d\u5de6\u79fb\u5230\u7ea6 0.20x\uff0c\u800c\u907f\u514d\u91cd\u8e48 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` \u7684\u8d28\u91cf\u5d29\u584c\uff1b\u82e5 FVU \u4ecd\u660e\u663e\u4f18\u4e8e r114 \u5e76\u5c3d\u91cf\u63a5\u8fd1 r116\uff0c\u5219\u8bf4\u660e\u5728\u5f53\u524d target \u4e0a\uff0c\u8fdb\u4e00\u6b65\u538b\u6bcf-expert \u5bbd\u5ea6\u6bd4\u538b active experts \u66f4\u503c\u5f97\u4f5c\u4e3a `<0.25x` \u4e3b\u7ebf\u7ee7\u7eed\u63a8\u8fdb\u3002",
