research/history/logs/agent_round_0135.stdout.log:580:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM","value":"128"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=Bx 是共享低秩投影，U={u_i} 是静态 shared library，{B_e} 是静态 routed expert 子库。在线侧仍可导出为“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + routed expert local top-k + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 判定为直接兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设：相对 r134 仅把 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 从 192 进一步降到 128，在保持 `K=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 与其余训练配方不变时，shared low-rank basis 仍能承担主要全局结构，从而把总成本从约 0.35x 继续压到约 0.32x；如果 FVU 仍接近 r134 的 0.1248，则说明当前最有希望的低成本结构段就是这条 hetero MoE 线的进一步低秩压缩。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=128` 在约 0.32x 下仍接近 r134，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `K=96` 或 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=256`，继续测试这条 hetero MoE 线能否再向左推进。","如果该点明显退化，则说明 shared branch 的 low-rank 压缩已经接近极限，后续不应继续在该 family 上细扫 hidden width，而应切回新的结构假设。","真实训练启动后先检查 `research/history/logs/round*.config.json` 与 checkpoint `config.json` 中 `factorized_hidden_dim=128` 已落盘，再解释结果。"],"notes_to_memory":["本地 allowlist 校验已通过：`shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 允许 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` param-only override。","本地 smoke 已通过：`ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk, K=128, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=128, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 可 instantiate/forward/backward。","当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 下，该 matched recipe 估算 selection≈0.20x、deployment≈0.12x、total≈0.32x，低于 r134 的 0.35x，也低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。"],"reference_round":134,"self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r134 只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`。r134 已证明这条 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 线在 0.35x 仍保持接近 r129 的质量，继续把 shared scorer 从 192 压到 128 是当前信息增量最高、且仍符合“进一步稀疏化 + 进一步低秩化”指引的动作。主要风险是该点会被现有 0.30x-0.35x anchor 支配；但这正是本轮要确认的压缩边界。","summary":"Round 135 继续沿当前最有希望的 hetero MoE 线做一次更激进但仍清晰的单变量低秩压缩。以 r134 为 reference，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=128`，直接测试 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 能否在约 0.32x 总成本下维持接近当前最强低成本结构点的质量。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0139.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_perf_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ACTIVE_EXPERTS","value":"1"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual","family_stage":"stabilize","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{j∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j} + Σ_{m∈S_res(x-x_stage1)} γ_m(x) c_m，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx)，U={u_i} 是 shared 静态向量库，{B_e} 是 routed expert 静态子库，C={c_m} 是全局 residual 静态库，x_stage1 为 shared+routed stage 的重构。在线导出链路仍是“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + 单 expert local top-k + residual library lookup + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此该 family 判定为扩展兼容，不是不兼容 family。唯一主假设：相对 r138 仅把 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 从 2 降到 1，保持 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual`、`K=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 与其余训练配方不变，利用 residual cleanup 吃掉少掉的第二个 routed expert 覆盖，从而把 total_cost 从约 0.60x 压到约 0.52x，同时尽量保住 r138 的 FVU=0.0946，回答这条 hetero MoE + residual 线能否在 0.5x 左右形成新的结构性 Pareto 段。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 仍接近 r138 的 FVU，则下一轮保持该 family 不变，只改 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 或 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 继续向 <0.5x 压缩。","如果 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 明显掉点，则说明这条线当前仍依赖双 expert 覆盖，下一轮优先回到 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`，只改 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 做 matched-cost 容量压缩，而不是继续削 router path。","若训练前 override 校验再次失败，应先检查 family-specific allowlist 是否被 runtime 热加载到最新代码，而不要把失败误判成架构结论。"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际落盘修复 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` 的 AutoResearch override allowlist，真实改动仅在 `research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py`。","本地校验通过：`validate_env_overrides(..., fallback_architecture='shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual')` 现在接受 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`、`STAGE1_RATIO`，同时仍拒绝未消费的 `TRUNK_RANK`。","成本自检：在 r138 配方下把 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 设为 1 后，selection_accesses=1646592、deployment_accesses=524288、combined_accesses=2170880，对当前 1024x4096 proxy 的 combined_ratio≈0.52，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。"],"reference_round":138,"self_review":"先修真实 blocker，再发实验：r138 已证明 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` 有结构价值，但此前它没有接入 family-specific override allowlist，后续任何合法的单变量 param-only 探针都会在训练前被判为 disallowed。当前已实际补上该 wiring，并做了本地 allowlist 自检。计划运行时相对 r138 只改 1 个 env 参数 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS`，满足单变量原则；风险是第二个 routed expert 仍对当前 target 很关键，导致 FVU 回退，但这会直接回答 residual stage 是否足以支撑更轻的 expert 激活路径。","summary":"已实际修复 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` 的参数接线 blocker，使该新 family 后续可以合法做单变量 param-only 探针。建议本轮以 r138 为 reference，只改 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1`，直接测试“shared low-rank basis + 单 routed expert + residual cleanup”能否把这条 hetero MoE 线从约 0.60x 压到约 0.52x total_cost，并保持足够接近 r138 的质量。","touched_files":["research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py"]}
research/history/round_summaries/round_0048.json:17:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_{r=1..R} \u03b2_r(x) u_r + \u03a3_{i\u2208S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} \u03b1_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d t(x)=\u03a3_{r=1..R} \u03b2_r(x) u_r\u3002\u4e5f\u5c31\u662f\u5148\u7528\u9759\u6001 low-rank trunk \u5411\u91cf\u5e93 U={u_r} \u91cd\u6784\u5e73\u6ed1\u4e3b\u5e72\uff0c\u518d\u5bf9\u6b8b\u5dee\u7528\u8f7b\u91cf router \u9009\u62e9\u5355\u4e2a\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93 B_e={b_{e,i}} \u5e76\u505a\u5c40\u90e8 sparse \u9009\u62e9\uff1b\u56e0\u6b64\u5b83\u4ecd\u53ef\u76f4\u63a5\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u201ctrunk \u67e5\u8868 + expert \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 + \u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c\u201d\u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\u3002Round 43 \u7684 blocker \u4e0d\u662f\u7ed3\u6784\u8d28\u91cf\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u8fd0\u884c\u65f6\u89c2\u6d4b\u8def\u5f84\u9519\u8bef\uff1a`from sparsify import SparseCoder` \u76f4\u63a5\u5b9e\u4f8b\u5316\u65f6\u6ca1\u6709\u5c0a\u91cd `cfg.architecture`\uff0c\u5bfc\u81f4 policy behavioral-diff \u5b9e\u9645\u5728\u6bd4\u8f83 topk vs topk\uff0c\u8bef\u628a `lowrank_expert_topk` \u5224\u6210\u4e0e topk \u5b8c\u5168\u76f8\u540c\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u53ea\u4fee\u590d `sparsify/` \u5185\u7684\u6784\u9020\u5206\u53d1\uff0c\u4f7f\u76f4\u63a5\u6784\u9020 `SparseCoder(..., cfg)` \u65f6\u4e5f\u80fd\u6309 `cfg.architecture` \u8fd4\u56de\u6b63\u786e family\uff0c\u7136\u540e\u6309 r43 \u7684\u539f\u8bbe\u8ba1\u91cd\u8dd1\u76f8\u5bf9 r42 \u4ec5\u6539 `TRUNK_RANK=128` \u7684\u4f4e\u6210\u672c probe\uff0c\u9a8c\u8bc1\u8fd9\u6761 `lowrank + expert` \u7ed3\u6784\u5728\u7ea6 0.44x total_cost \u4e0b\u662f\u5426\u771f\u80fd\u5f62\u6210\u65b0\u7684 Pareto \u6bb5\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0048.json:18:    "summary": "\u5f53\u524d\u4f18\u5148\u7ea7\u6700\u9ad8\u7684\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u5728 `lowrank_expert_residual` \u4e0a\u505a\u7b2c\u56db\u4e2a\u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u90bb\u57df\u70b9\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u5148\u4fee\u6389 Round 43 \u66b4\u9732\u51fa\u7684\u7cfb\u7edf blocker\uff1a`lowrank_expert_topk` \u88ab policy \u7684 behavioral diff \u8bef\u62e6\u3002\u4fee\u590d `SparseCoder` \u7684\u76f4\u63a5\u6784\u9020\u5206\u53d1\u540e\uff0c\u6309\u539f\u8ba1\u5212\u91cd\u8dd1 r43 \u7684 `TRUNK_RANK=128` \u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u9a8c\u8bc1\uff0c\u53ef\u4ee5\u5728\u4e0d\u5f15\u5165\u65b0 tunable \u7684\u524d\u63d0\u4e0b\u91cd\u65b0\u56de\u7b54 `lowrank + expert` \u8fd9\u6761\u9ad8\u4f18\u5148\u7ea7\u7ed3\u6784\u7ebf\u662f\u5426\u503c\u5f97\u7ee7\u7eed\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0048.json:23:    "self_review": "\u6ee1\u8db3\u5f53\u524d\u9636\u6bb5\u7684\u8fd0\u884c\u65f6\u4f18\u5148\u7ea7\uff1a\u5148\u4fee blocker\uff0c\u518d\u505a\u7ed3\u6784\u6bd4\u8f83\u3002\u4ee3\u7801\u6539\u52a8\u9650\u5236\u5728 `sparsify/`\uff0c\u4e0d\u78b0 evaluation semantics\uff0c\u4e5f\u4e0d\u6539 AutoResearch/launcher\uff1b\u771f\u6b63\u5b9e\u9a8c\u914d\u7f6e\u76f8\u5bf9 r42 \u4ecd\u53ea\u6539\u4e00\u4e2a env \u53c2\u6570 `TRUNK_RANK=128`\u3002\u8fd9\u6b21 repair \u7684\u76ee\u6807\u4e0d\u662f\u6539\u8bad\u7ec3\u8bed\u4e49\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u8ba9\u516c\u5171\u6784\u9020\u5165\u53e3\u4e0e `cfg.architecture` \u4e00\u81f4\uff0c\u907f\u514d\u518d\u6b21\u628a policy \u8bef\u5224\u5f53\u6210\u7ed3\u6784\u7ed3\u8bba\u3002\u98ce\u9669\u662f\u4fee\u590d\u540e `lowrank_expert_topk` \u7684\u771f\u5b9e\u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u6548\u679c\u53ef\u80fd\u4ecd\u7136\u4e00\u822c\uff1b\u4f46\u90a3\u65f6\u624d\u80fd\u628a\u5b83\u5f53\u6210\u7ed3\u6784\u8bc1\u636e\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u89c2\u6d4b\u94fe\u8def\u4f2a\u5f71\u3002",
